data.text: @AatifNawaz @TheRealPCB @thePSLt20 Mujhy yeh bta konsi political isolation or konsi geopolitical exile? Apny masters ko khush karny k liye wahan beth k achi chezon ko bhi kisi gashti ki trah moot daal k bta rha tu khoti k bachy. Lakh di lanat tery ty. Allah kary tujhy wahin maut aye aur yeh miiti naseeb na ho.
@AatifNawaz @TheRealPCB @thePSLt20 O kisi khoti k bachy... Keri isolation ty keri geopolitical exile? Patwari kuttay ka bacha e hota hai sabit kardiya tu ny.

@AatifNawaz @TheRealPCB @thePSLt20 It's so heartwarming to see such an incredible tournament held in our homeland. Our people have suffered a lot due to obvious reasons. May this happiness and joy continue for all of us.
@AatifNawaz @TheRealPCB @thePSLt20 Jitna bhi PCB aur Franchises ko appreciate kiya jaye kam hai.
@AatifNawaz @TheRealPCB @thePSLt20 Aatif thanks for your 'PSL in 2 minutes'. Will miss that
@AatifNawaz @TheRealPCB @thePSLt20 In shaa Allah next one hope to see you in the ground Aatif, hopefully as a commentator!
